OL,3,CVisually impaired islanders get crafty
OL,4,Cfor Christmas
OL,6,FJersey islanders with visual
OL,7,Fimpairments have been treated to some
OL,8,Ffestive fun in the run-up to Christmas.
OL,10,FEyecan clients have been making
OL,11,Ffestive wreaths using plenty of
OL,12,Flocally sourced foliage to cover their
OL,13,Fdecorations.
OL,15,FThe charity has more than 500 people
OL,16,Fon its books, but regularly supports
OL,17,F50 every week - all who live with some
OL,18,Fvariation of visual impairment.
OL,20,FStella Picot is one person who comes
OL,21,Fto the Westlea Centre every week.
