OL,3,CVisually impaired islanders get crafty
OL,4,Cfor Christmas
OL,6,FShe has Macular Degeneration: a
OL,7,Fcondition which slowly blurs - and in
OL,8,Fextreme cases - stops vision entirely.
OL,10,FStella was diagnosed three years ago
OL,11,Fand says: "I gave up driving myself
OL,12,Fbecause as we were going up the hill,
OL,13,FI thought I saw somebody along the
OL,14,Fedge.
OL,16,F"I did think, I shouldn't be driving
OL,17,Fthen, because I thought 'No, I really
OL,18,Fcan't see that person there'."
