OL,3,CVisually impaired islanders get crafty
OL,4,Cfor Christmas
OL,6,FOlwyn Ruellan is also a regular
OL,7,Fvisitor to the hub in St Martin and
OL,8,Ftold ITV News the impact the charity's
OL,9,Fwork has had on her confidence:
OL,11,FHe explains: "I wasn't going out, I
OL,12,Fdidn't want to go out anywhere.
OL,14,F"That completely changed. Here they
OL,15,Fhelp me so much and helped me realise,
OL,16,Fyou know, I wasn't the only person."
OL,18,FMark Coxshall, CEO of Eyecan Jersey,
OL,19,Fsaid that the clients have always been
OL,20,Fthe focus of their work in the
OL,21,Fcommunity.
