OL,3,CVisually impaired islanders get crafty
OL,4,Cfor Christmas
OL,6,FMark said: "This is a great
OL,7,Fopportunity really to show that sight
OL,8,Floss is no barrier, and you can
OL,9,Factually see by the quality of the
OL,10,Fwork during the morning, it's
OL,11,Fabsolutely fantastic.
OL,13,F"I think moreover this is about social
OL,14,Factivity for our members. It's about
OL,15,Fmembers supporting each other and
OL,16,Fdeveloping those peer support
OL,17,Fnetworks, which is really one of our
OL,18,Fbig aspirations."
