OL,3,CVisually impaired islanders get crafty
OL,4,Cfor Christmas
OL,6,FThe charity wants more islanders to be
OL,7,Faware of its services, to ensure all
OL,8,Fthose who need assistance can access
OL,9,Fthe help.
OL,11,FMark continued: "Eyecan is the only
OL,12,Fsight loss charity working on island.
OL,14,F"We just want to make sure that people
OL,15,Fhave those necessities, to help them
OL,16,Flive their strongest lives -
OL,17,Fparticularly when they've been
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with sight loss and they
OL,19,Fhave all of those fears and anxieties
OL,20,Fthat come with that."
